# Publishing Checklist

## Pre-Publish Requirements
- [ ] `publisher` field set in package.json
- [ ] Meaningful `displayName` and `description`
- [ ] Icon added (128x128 PNG recommended)
- [ ] README.md with features, screenshots, usage
- [ ] CHANGELOG.md updated
- [ ] `repository` URL in package.json
- [ ] License file present
- [ ] All tests passing

## .vscodeignore Template
```
.vscode/**
.vscode-test/**
src/**
.gitignore
.yarnrc
vsc-extension-quickstart.md
**/tsconfig.json
**/.eslintrc.json
**/*.map
**/*.ts
!dist/**
node_modules/**
```

## Publishing Commands
```bash
# Login (first time only)
vsce login <publisher-name>

# Test package locally
vsce package

# Publish
vsce publish

# Publish with version bump
vsce publish patch  # 1.0.0 -> 1.0.1
vsce publish minor  # 1.0.0 -> 1.1.0
vsce publish major  # 1.0.0 -> 2.0.0
```

## Marketplace Optimization
- Use relevant `categories` in package.json
- Add `keywords` for searchability
- Include screenshots in README
- Write clear, concise descriptions